title: LEGO Valentines Cupid Dog Building Kit Just $9.99 (New Release – Order Quick!)
text:
What a cute item to snag for Valentine’s Day! ❤️
Hop on over to Amazon.com where you can grab this newly-released LEGO Bricks & More Valentines Cupid Dog Building Kit for just $9.99! This set includes over 145 pieces and is designed for ages 7 and up.
This is a great buy so act fast! This same item is priced at OVER $24 on Walmart.com .
